videos.headline: Mcelroy gets to the outside for Colorado State TD
videos.description: Marcus McElroy Jr. takes the handoff and navigates to the sideline to dive into the end zone for a 15-yard Colorado State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mcelroy gets to the outside for Colorado State TD) 2020/10/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fresno State's Rivers runs through a defender to score a 32-yard TD
videos.description: Ronnie Rivers crashes through a Colorado State defender as he reaches the sideline and makes his way into the end zone to score a 32-yard touchdown and help Fresno State take a 17-10 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fresno State's Rivers runs through a defender to score a 32-yard TD) 2020/10/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fresno State's Wheatfall leaps to make athletic grab over a defender
videos.description: Jake Haener goes deep to Keric Wheatfall who leaps to make a difficult grab around a Colorado State defender along the sideline for an amazing 38-yard reception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fresno State's Wheatfall leaps to make athletic grab over a defender) 2020/10/29 ESHEET
